snippet.title: Arcadia Fallen II Kickstarter
snippet.description:
A new adventure begins!
The Kickstarter for Arcadia Fallen II is LIVE‼️🥳

Become a student at the magical Seven Winds Academy, and uncover its secrets.
Prep for finals, fall in love and maybe start a revolution...

Read more and play the demo here🤗
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/galdra/arcadia-fallen-2
